Ruff Ryders’ first lady, Eve has welcomed her first child with hubby Maximillion Cooper. The American rapper and actress took to Instagram on Thursday to announce that she has welcomed a bouncing baby boy with her husband. The 43-year-old new mom posted an adorable snap of her newborn baby with the caption: “Our Beautiful boy was born Feb 1st 2022.   Daddy Freeze, Seun Kuti react to Bible unscathed in fire…     Alesh raises the alarm over fake drinks in clubs     Seun Kuti knocks colleagues over Oxlade’s s3x tape   “Wilde Wolf Fife Alexander Somers Cooper. Words can’t describe this feeling.” - Advertisement - In October 2021, Eve confirmed her pregnancy for the first time by showing off photos of her growing baby bump and sharing that she and her British husband of more than seven years had been “waiting for this blessing.” Eve and Maximillion started dating in 2010 and got married in 2014.